<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Ghost Hunter License</title>
    <style>
        /* Brown background for the whole page */
        body { font-family: sans-serif; background-color: brown; color: black; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }

        /* Main container designed to look like an old file folder */
        .container { 
            width: 600px; margin: auto;background-color: wheat; padding: 25px; border: 5px solid saddlebrown; 
        }

        /* General spacing for sections */
        header, section { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        
        /* Navigation bar with borders and centered links */
        nav { 
            text-align: center;border-top: 2px solid saddlebrown; border-bottom: 2px solid saddlebrown;padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        nav a { color: saddlebrown; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px; }

        /* Form styling for a clean look */
        form { text-align: left; margin: auto; width: 90%; }
        
        label { font-weight: bold; color: saddlebrown; }

        input, textarea { 
            width: 100%; margin-bottom: 15px;  background-color: white; border: 1px solid saddlebrown;padding: 8px; box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        /* Submit button: Blue, bold, and centered */
        .submit-btn { 
            color: blue; font-weight: bold;background-color: white; border: 2px solid blue; padding: 10px 25px; cursor: pointer; width: auto;
        }

        /* Footer styling on the right */
        footer { 
            text-align: right; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 10px;  border-top: 1px solid saddlebrown; font-size: small;
        }

        /* List styling for License Info */
        ul { list-style-type: circle; padding-left: 40px; text-align: left; }
        li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

    <header>
        <h1 style="color: saddlebrown;">Ghost Hunter License</h1>
        <p><strong>Official Paranormal Investigator Permit</strong></p>
    </header>

    <nav>
        <a href="https://www.paralearning.org/courses/practical-ghost-hunting/">License Info</a> | 
        <a href="mailto:example@gmail.com">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <section>
        <h3>About This Website</h3>
        <p>This website explains the Ghost Hunter License. It is a fictional permit for people who investigate paranormal activity and supernatural events.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h3 style="color: saddlebrown;">License Information</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Investigator Name:</strong> Amir Adem</li>
            <li><strong>License Number:</strong> 101-GHOST-99</li>
            <li><strong>Investigation Area:</strong> Ethiopia</li>
            <li><strong>Expiration Date:</strong> October 31, 2030</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <hr style="border: 1px solid saddlebrown;">

    <section>
        <h3>Apply for a Ghost Hunter License</h3>
        <form>
            <label>Full Name:</label>
            <input type="text" name="name">
            
            <label>Email Address:</label>
            <input type="text" name="email">
            
            <label>Investigation Area (City):</label>
            <input type="text" name="city">
            
            <label>Experience Level:</label>
            <input type="text" name="experience">
            
            <label>Reason for Applying:</label>
            <textarea rows="4"></textarea>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <input type="submit" value="Submit Application" class="submit-btn">
            </div>
        </form>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>Grade 11 Web Design Assignment</p>
        <p>Created by Amir A.</p>
    </footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>
